Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:19.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,風　強っ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:20.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,寒い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:22.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,完全に秋だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.37,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ねっ　そういえばさ　知ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:25.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なになに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:32.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,熱っ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:36.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もうあったかいの季節か
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.09,0:00:41.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,世間はすっかり秋の様相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,季節は流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.38,0:00:46.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私を置き去りにして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:49.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いたいた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:51.37,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,安楽岡さーん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:58.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,この前の文化祭の係決めのとき　休んでたでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ステージ係になっちゃったんだけど　いいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:05.38,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ステ…　何すれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:10.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ああ　全然　搬入とかは軽音部のやつにやらせるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:14.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,タイムスケジュール管理とか簡単なことしかないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:16.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お願ーい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:21.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから　行ってこいっつってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:26.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まっ　いっか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:27.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:31.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やったー　これで係埋まった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ありがとう　安楽岡さん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:45.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう熱くないや
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:02.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:38.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんの式は春休みにやるんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,丁寧にも本人が直接知らせに来たのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:46.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:51.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おめでとう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:56.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,帰り道　少し話した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦のやつ　駄目だったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いい気味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:04.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,急でびっくりした？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ううん　全然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:08.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:12.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,皆川先生のこと好きなの　バレバレだったから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:19.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それより　眼鏡やめたんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:24.37,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,眼鏡壊しちゃって　ついでに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,コンタクトにしてって言われたんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,な…なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.32,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,バレバレ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:34.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私は眼鏡の方がよかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:36.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だって…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:42.72,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今のお兄ちゃんは　昔のお兄ちゃんを思い出して
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,少し胸が苦しいから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:51.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,式　来てくれるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:11.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,当たり前じゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:19.78,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:38.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はい　じゃあこれが本番のタイムスケジュール最終版
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:43.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,前日までの準備で疲れてると思うけど　頑張りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:47.25,UP JP,,0,0,0,,みんなそれぞれの出番まで自由行動ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.86,UP JP,,0,0,0,,時間厳守でお願いしまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:46.66,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おいおい　リーダー目ぇ据わってるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:50.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,このステージ設営にやたら気合入れてたからなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おい　そこの男子生徒Ａ　Ｂ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:56.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,遅刻しやがったら　後夜祭のキャンプファイアにぶっ込むからな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:59.30,UP JP,,0,0,0,,いやあ　何とか形になりそうでよかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,では　一時解散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:05:59.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,800,0,,おーい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:02.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,迎え来ちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,彼氏と回るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,遅刻すんなよー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なに　時間ないの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,大丈夫大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何かもう疲れちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　どっかで休もうか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:16.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やだー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,誰といたいかなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:24.78,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,頭に浮かんだ幾つかの選択肢は　そっとしまい込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どこから見る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まず　何か食べようよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:29.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,賛成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:33.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ステージ担当の時間まで暇だな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.72,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,よろしくお願いしまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ファッションショーやってまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ぜひとも見ていってください
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すてきな作品がいっぱいですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:41.78,UP JP,,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.50,UP JP,,0,0,0,,遅い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.24,UP JP,,0,0,0,,何やってた　もう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早く　終わっちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:31.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私の方がずっと長く　真っすぐに麦を好きだったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すごーい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だからすっきりしてんの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あんたも自分だけで歩いてみたら分かるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:53.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:56.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すっごくよかったよ　鴎端さんの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ホント？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:08:00.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,刺しゅう　細かすぎ　全部自分でやったの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.32,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すごーい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:05.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もしかして　いつも着てる服も手作り？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そうだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:10.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やっぱりそうだったんだ　前から聞いてみたかったんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:13.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ねえ　今度作り方教えて　のり子ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私もお願い　のり子ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:17.74,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,最可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:19.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私はまだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.66,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,遅いよ　安楽岡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,さっさとみんなを手伝いな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,800,0,,ヤベえ　もう始まるって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,800,0,0,,ねえ　あれ　どっちの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:34.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,800,0,,間に合わない　照明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:34.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,200,0,,さっさと動く
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,600,0,0,,は…はい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,安楽岡さん　配線コード持ってきて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:39.38,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:42.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ごめん　安楽岡さん　チラシ配り手伝って
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:43.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:46.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,安楽岡　そこの機材　裏にはけといて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ど…どれですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それ　早く
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,は…はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,失礼します
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,誰もいない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,疲れた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:13.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,一人は心地いい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,一人はいろんなことが見えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:22.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だってもともと　一人だったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,一人が怖い？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ううん　今はもう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:34.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,元から一人だし　みんな一人だから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　これにも意味なんてないか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ないよ　ない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:55.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃあなぜ　私たちはあの日　約束したんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どうして…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,寝ちゃってた？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,肩凝った
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:27.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.12,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私たちは出会ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:52.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はーい　有志の方は終業式終わりに集まって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:11:01.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう　たかが先生同士の結婚祝いに　超重労働じゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:04.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,しゃべってないできりきり動いて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:05.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,実行チームでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:09.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいから　そこのもう使わない工具　裏に戻しておいて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えー　また？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから早く
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.37,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:18.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,安楽岡さん　俺も手伝うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:19.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おっととと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あ…ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:23.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:27.37,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,自分　森山って言います　今年から同じクラスで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:43.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あの　安楽岡さん　早く荷物…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ありがとう　手伝ってくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,助かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あ…あの　安楽岡さん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.74,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,最近　粟屋とはどうなの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:03.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ここんとこ　あんまり二人でいないみたいだし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:07.10,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あの　安楽岡さん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もしよかったら　俺と…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:10.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はいはい　そこまで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.22,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火は私んだから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,うかつにアピールしないでくれる？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ちょっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:20.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,行こっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:28.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ご…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.40,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっ　えっちゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,大丈夫　さっきのは冗談だから
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,な…なんであんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まだしばらく　言い寄られたくないでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.72,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なんで泣くのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:13.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,や…優しい…　えっちゃん優しい…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:16.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はいはい　分かったから鼻かんで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:21.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,も…もう　話し掛けてくれないかと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そんなわけないじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ごめんね　時間かかって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,髪切ったんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あっ　入試のときの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今日はおさげじゃないんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,触ってみてもいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:57.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,髪　サラッサラ　下ろして正解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:06.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そのとき私は　なぜだか許された気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まるで初めて息するみたいに　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:15.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,世界が私を受け入れて　そして…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:26.12,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,その髪型も似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,さっぱりしたー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おめでとうございまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.38,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,こういうのもいいもんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いやあ　恥ずかしい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.32,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,これ　みんなからの寄せ書きです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:11.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,安楽岡さん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:16.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,安楽岡さんは先生たちの結婚式　行くんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:19.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:22.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私まだ結婚式って行ったことない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私も初めて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:34.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やっぱ憧れるよね　大好きな人と一生を添い遂げる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:38.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,憧れる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ブーケトスよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:10.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ト…トスって　投げてないじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:11.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,受け取って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何で私に…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,茜さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:22.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,次は　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.37,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,とられちゃ駄目よ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:30.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,よ…余計なお世話です
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃねー
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,バイバーイ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:44.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あの日の約束にも　積み重ねた日々にも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,意味なんてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:02.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,初めはたださみしくて　触れたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:11.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,君の熱に　焦がれた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:15.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花火…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:21.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私たちがかつて交わした契約
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:26.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,二人とも　恋に敗れた今
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:31.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ねえ　契約はもう無効？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:37.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それとも　新しい契約をもしも結べるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:40.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,謝んな　バーカ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:02.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,言っとくけど　茜さんは変わったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:04.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はいはい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.84,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,分かってるって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:10.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんが最後に選んだんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:12.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私が間違ってたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:18.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それくらいには私はお兄ちゃんのこと　好きだったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,言葉にしても　平気
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:33.66,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦も　よく頑張ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:42.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お前も
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:47.66,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私たちは初めて触れあうことを避けて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:52.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,言葉を選んで相手を思いやることをしている気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それは今までしてこなかったことだった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いろんなことを話した
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:04.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,たくさん　今までの分も
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:12.10,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何か　長かったなぁ　初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:15.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,初恋はかなわないっていうしな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:20.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,日は秋なのに　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:24.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,暖かく差し込んで　ほこりを照らして　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:31.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,空気の流れは緩やかで　使い古した木のにおいがして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:34.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,時間は永遠で一瞬で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:38.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私は静かに息を吸い込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:42.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,決意をした
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:00.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私…　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:05.84,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦に出会えて　よかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私たちは本物を探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:19.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それが簡単に手に入らないことを知っている
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:24.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どんなに願っても祈っても　届かないものかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今度はもっと　傷つくかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:35.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それは私たちをもっと　孤独にするかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:40.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:45.84,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,求め続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:49.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,このまま
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:50.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,離れたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:51.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,離さないでほしい　ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:56.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,引き留めたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,終わりたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,引き留めてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:01.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,終わらせたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:05.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でも　さよなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:11.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今　救われなくてもそれでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:14.75,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私たちは本物を探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.81,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そのために　生きていく
Comment: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,----------TEXT_CN----------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.06,0:00:19.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好大的风
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.52,0:00:20.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真冷
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.80,0:00:22.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,已经入秋啦
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.37,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,有件新鲜事 你听说没有
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.72,0:00:25.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.38,0:00:32.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.64,0:00:36.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都该喝热饮了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.09,0:00:41.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,眼前一派秋天的景象
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,季节匆匆流逝
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.38,0:00:46.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,独留我伫立在原地
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.70,0:00:49.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.96,0:00:51.37,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.80,0:00:58.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,之前分配文化节职务的时候 你不是没来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,然后你就被派去负责舞台部分了 可以吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.54,0:01:05.38,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,舞台… 需要我做什么…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.72,0:01:10.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,别担心 搬东西这种粗活会交给轻音部的人去做
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.32,0:01:14.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你只用做些简单的工作 比如把控进度之类的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.85,0:01:16.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.93,0:01:21.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以我才叫你赶紧去啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.10,0:01:26.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.46,0:01:27.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我来做
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.57,0:01:31.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,太好了 这下人都找齐了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.42,0:01:45.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,转眼就变凉了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.66,0:02:02.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,麦…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.38,0:03:38.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,哥哥的婚礼会在春假期间举行
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.21,0:03:42.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这是他亲自上门通知我们的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.05,0:03:46.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.81,0:03:51.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.32,0:03:56.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,送他回去的路上 我们聊了几句
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,麦这家伙 原来被甩了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.18,0:04:01.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.81,0:04:04.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,突然听到很意外吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不会啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.84,0:04:08.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.78,0:04:12.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你对皆川老师的喜欢都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.22,0:04:19.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,话说 你怎么不戴眼镜了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.77,0:04:24.37,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我把眼镜弄坏了 干脆就不戴了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,肯定是她叫你戴隐形眼镜的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你…你怎么知道
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.32,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.66,0:04:34.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我还是喜欢看你戴框架眼镜
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.00,0:04:36.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.09,0:04:42.72,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,现在的哥哥 让我想起了以前的哥哥
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,心里有点苦闷
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.98,0:04:51.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你会来参加我的婚礼吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.54,0:05:11.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我会去的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这还用问
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.90,0:05:19.78,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.66,0:05:38.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,听着 我手里拿的就是最终的正式节目单
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.22,0:05:43.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我知道大家忙到现在肯定很累了 再加把油啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.97,0:05:47.25,UP CN,,0,0,0,,大家可以在开场前自由活动
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.86,UP CN,,0,0,0,,但请严格遵守时限
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.81,0:05:46.66,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,快看快看 大姐大都两眼发直了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.66,0:05:50.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,她为了布置舞台的事可是操碎了心啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喂 那边的男生A和男生B
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.97,0:05:56.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,要是敢迟到的话 我就在闭幕晚会上把你们扔进篝火里
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.58,0:05:59.30,UP CN,,0,0,0,,还好还好 总算是像点样子了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那就先解散吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.72,0:05:59.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,800,0,,我在这
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.80,0:06:02.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,他来接我了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你要和男朋友逛啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,记得别迟到哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么 没空吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,有空有空
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,人家现在觉得好累
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,要找个地方休息一下吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.57,0:06:16.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我想和谁一起逛呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.08,0:06:24.78,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,脑海中浮现出了几个选项 又被我逐一否定
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,从哪开始逛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,先去吃点东西吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.44,0:06:29.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.00,0:06:33.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,开场前也没什么事可做
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.72,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,欢迎大家来捧场
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们正在举办时装秀
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,走过路过不要错过
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都是些很棒的作品哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.81,0:06:41.78,UP CN,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.50,UP CN,,0,0,0,,怎么才来
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.24,UP CN,,0,0,0,,干什么去了 真是的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,快进去 要结束了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.66,0:07:31.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我对麦的喜欢 可比你长久得多 真诚得多
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以我现在一身轻松
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你也试着自己走一走就明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.17,0:07:53.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,感谢观赏
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.65,0:07:56.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,鸥端同学 你这身衣服特别棒
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.05,0:08:00.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,上面的刺绣太精致了 都是你自己缝的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.32,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.56,0:08:05.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,难道你平时穿的衣服也是自己做的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.73,0:08:10.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我果然没猜错 这个问题我早就想问了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.70,0:08:13.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,下次教我怎么做吧 典子
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是最可
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,也教教我吧 典子
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.82,0:08:17.74,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,叫我最可
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.82,0:08:19.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我还是老样子…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.66,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,慢死了 安乐冈
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,赶紧去给大家帮忙
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,800,0,,糟了 要开始了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,800,0,0,,喂 那个放哪里
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.93,0:08:34.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,800,0,,来不及了 照明
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.52,0:08:34.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,200,0,,还不动起来
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,600,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学 把电线拿过来
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.42,0:08:39.38,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.38,0:08:42.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉 安乐冈同学 帮我发下传单
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.09,0:08:43.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.86,0:08:46.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,安乐冈 把那个器材搬到后面去
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,哪…哪个
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那个 快点
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没人
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.33,0:09:13.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,一个人很自在
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,一个人能看清很多事
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.64,0:09:22.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我本来就是孤身一人
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你害怕一个人吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不 现在不怕了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.52,0:09:34.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我本来就是一个人 大家都是一个人
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以 这样做也没有意义吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没有 都没有
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.65,0:09:55.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那我们那天为什么要许下约定呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我睡着了？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,肩膀好酸
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.26,0:10:27.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.12,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,要让我们相遇呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.02,0:10:52.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,注意 想参加的同学请在结业典礼后集合
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.92,0:11:01.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真是的 不就是庆祝老师结婚嘛 也太折腾人了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.78,0:11:04.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,废话少说 手脚麻利点
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.21,0:11:05.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你不是执行组的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.85,0:11:09.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好了 快把那些用完的工具搬回后面去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么又是我
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,叫你去你就去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.37,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.70,0:11:18.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学 我来帮你
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.65,0:11:19.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好险好险
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.52,0:11:23.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.45,0:11:27.37,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我叫森山 从今年起和你同班
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.82,0:11:43.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学 快把东西放下吧…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,谢谢你来帮我
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,幸亏有你
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,话…话说 安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.74,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你和粟屋最近怎么样
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.00,0:12:03.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这段时间很少见到你们俩在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.36,0:12:07.10,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话 请和我…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.68,0:12:10.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好了好了 到此为止
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.22,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,花火是我的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,能不能别乱给名花松土
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.22,0:12:20.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.38,0:12:28.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,对…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.40,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我还是要谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小…小绘…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,别介意 我刚才只是开个玩笑
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为…为什么要那么做…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你暂时还不想开始下一段 不是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.72,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你哭什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.69,0:13:13.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真…真好… 你对我真好…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.82,0:13:16.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好好好 我知道啦 快擦擦鼻涕
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.14,0:13:21.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我…我以为你再也不会跟我说话了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,对不起 让你久等了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你把头发剪了…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是你 我们入学考试时见过
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.52,0:13:45.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你今天没编辫子呀
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我能摸一下吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.80,0:13:57.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好顺滑的头发 披下来就对了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.85,0:14:06.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那一刻 我觉得自己得到了救赎
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,仿佛第一次有了呼吸
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.90,0:14:15.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,世界接纳了我 然后又…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小绘
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.09,0:14:26.12,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,短发也很适合你
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,如释重负
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,恭贺老师喜结良缘
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.38,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,热热闹闹的也不错呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,太难为情了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.32,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这是大家一起写的祝福语
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.74,0:15:11.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,安乐冈同学
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.12,0:15:16.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你肯定会去参加两位老师的婚礼吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.54,0:15:19.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.01,0:15:22.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我还没有参加过呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我也是第一次
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.17,0:15:34.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好期盼能和最爱的人携手共度余生啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.82,0:15:38.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我也期盼
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,送你捧花
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.56,0:16:10.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,还…还捧花呢 你连扔都没扔
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.65,0:16:11.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,快收下
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么要给我…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,别问了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,收就收
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小茜…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.82,0:16:22.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,下次
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.37,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,可别再被人抢走了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.21,0:16:30.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你…你管不着
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.76,0:16:44.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那天的约定 共度的时光
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,到头来都是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.45,0:17:02.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,最初渴望温存 只是因为寂寞
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.66,0:17:11.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你的热度 使我入迷
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.72,0:17:15.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,花火…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.56,0:17:21.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们曾经许下约定
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.21,0:17:26.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,如今我们都失恋了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.62,0:17:31.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那个约定还算数吗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.41,0:17:37.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,或者说 我们还可以许下新的约定
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.13,0:17:40.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,道什么歉 笨蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.62,0:18:02.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,跟你说一声 茜姐她已经变了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.05,0:18:04.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,行了行了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以说…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.84,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我心里有数
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.22,0:18:10.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,毕竟哥哥最终还是选择了她
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.93,0:18:12.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,一步错步步错
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.66,0:18:18.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我就是这么执着地喜欢着哥哥
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,可以坦然地说出口了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.66,0:18:33.66,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,麦 你是好样的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.61,0:18:42.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.69,0:18:47.66,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这似乎是我们第一次用谈话
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.36,0:18:52.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,而不是用肢体接触来安慰对方
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,至今从未有过这样的体验
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们漫无边际地聊着
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.80,0:19:04.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,把欠下的都补上了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.56,0:19:12.10,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我的初恋 还真是漫长啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.24,0:19:15.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不是都说初恋不会有结果吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.61,0:19:20.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,天已入秋
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.52,0:19:24.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,却有温暖的阳光洒进窗棂 照亮尘埃
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.32,0:19:31.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,缓慢流动的空气中 弥漫着陈木的味道
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.86,0:19:34.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,瞬间与永恒在此刻交错
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.33,0:19:38.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我静静地深吸一口气
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.60,0:19:42.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,做出了决定
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.66,0:20:00.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.04,0:20:05.84,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,能够遇见你 真的好幸运
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找真爱
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.69,0:20:19.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,也都知道真爱难寻
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.60,0:20:24.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,纵然虔诚祈祷千万遍 可能也走不进那个人的心
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,下次可能会伤得更深
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.84,0:20:35.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,种种伤害可能会使我们变得更加孤独
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.92,0:20:40.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,但终究…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.48,0:20:45.84,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,还要继续追寻
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.41,0:20:49.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不甘心
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.54,0:20:50.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,就这样分离
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.04,0:20:51.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,永远永远
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都不要离开我
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.24,0:20:56.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好想留住你
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不想走向结束
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,希望你能留住我
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.54,0:21:01.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不愿亲手结束
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.77,0:21:05.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,可只能 道一句珍重
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.52,0:21:11.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,现在还可以放任自己执迷不悟
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.41,0:21:14.75,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找真爱
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.81,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这就是我们生存的动力
